properties.areaDesc: Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI; Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI; Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 1 at 3:07AM CST until February 2 at 6:00PM CST by NWS Green Bay WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 kts with gusts up to 30 kts expected
after midnight. Waves 3 to 5 feet after midnight.

* WHERE...Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI, Sturgeon Bay
to Two Rivers WI and Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to 6 PM CST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 6 PM CST SUNDAY
